            "text": "Your identity card and proof of address.",
            "translation": "کارت شناسایی و مدرک آدرس."
        },
        {
            "order": 10,
            "person": 1,
            "text": "Here they are. How long will it take?",
            "translation": "بفرمایید. چقدر طول می‌کشد؟"
        },
